datasets.name: dataset_2
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('DAY', Event_Date_Time) AS Daily_Event_Date, SUM(New_Devices) AS New_Devices, SUM(SUM(New_Devices)) OVER (ORDER BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', Event_Date_Time) ROWS UNBOUNDED PRECEDING) AS Cumulative_New_Devices FROM hpx_events_model GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', Event_Date_Time) ORDER BY Daily_Event_Date

fields.name: Cumulative_New_Devices
fields.expression: SUM(SUM(New_Devices)) OVER (ORDER BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', Event_Date_Time) ROWS UNBOUNDED PRECEDING)

frame.title: New and Cumulative Devices Over Time
